Now over in the book of Hebrews, in the 10th chapter and beginning with the 19th verse, I'll read just for a portion of Scripture, about the 19th and 20th verses.
Having therefore, brethren, boldness to enter into the holiest by the blood of Jesus,
By a new and living way, which he has consecrated for us, through the veil, that is to say, his flesh;
And having a high priest over the house of God;
Now, may the Lord add His blessings to this reading of the Word. Now shall we bow our heads just a moment for prayer.
